From 9376570dcd80c09fb2bef2331db8c9efd13b3e84 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sun, 22 Feb 2026 15:16:27 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 31/42] Replace FrameSinkVideoCapturer with CALayerParams
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The capturer copied frames one by one,
Each pixel a toll on the CPU sun.
Now a context ID flies on XPC's wing—
Window Server composites everything.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
